            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>類似 Uber 的共乘車輛公司 Grab 在馬來西亞將會推出一款「車費競價」功能。乘客可直接向司機開價，將行程、價錢事先制定好，再由司機投標，並由乘客作最終確認。被選中的司機會收到詳細資料，並到乘客所在地接送客人。</p><p>Grab 的最新「車費競價」功能中，將允許乘客向司機開價，而不是根據 App 內顯示的費用來支付。乘客在 App 內制定好行程，以及提出理想價錢。同樣開啟了「競價車費」功能的司機們在收到乘客的要求後，可以直接「競標」，亦可提出更高的價格。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1206108" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/螢幕截圖-2023-11-22-18.53.28-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/螢幕截圖-2023-11-22-18.53.28-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/螢幕截圖-2023-11-22-18.53.28-1280x719.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/螢幕截圖-2023-11-22-18.53.28-768x431.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/螢幕截圖-2023-11-22-18.53.28-1536x863.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/螢幕截圖-2023-11-22-18.53.28.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>而乘客可檢視有哪些司機競標，或者司機給予的最新報價，並選擇其中一個司機。乘客接受後，司機將在 15 至 20 秒內收到通知。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1206109" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/螢幕截圖-2023-11-22-18.53.17-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/螢幕截圖-2023-11-22-18.53.17-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/螢幕截圖-2023-11-22-18.53.17-1280x719.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/螢幕截圖-2023-11-22-18.53.17-768x431.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/螢幕截圖-2023-11-22-18.53.17-1536x862.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/螢幕截圖-2023-11-22-18.53.17.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>目前 Grab 只會在指定地區進行小規模測試，他們指通過這個功能，創造一個更具透明性、更靈活的定價系統。Grab 並未公佈此功能正式推出的時間及推廣至更多城市的日程。</p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://forum.lowyat.net/topic/5421751#">Lowyat</a> via <a href="https://zinggadget.com/2023/11/22/grab%E5%B0%86%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA%E8%BD%A6%E8%B4%B9%E7%AB%9E%E4%BB%B7%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD/?fbclid=IwAR34mLeAxAMsqrh0_Qbqqc8QuZ8GuFtXum0kJNJvGHogMWrrzsHFlMlfdH8">Zing Gadget</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div>

