        <item>
            <title>Sam Altman 正式回歸 OpenAI   OpenAI 董事局大換血</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/11/22/sam-altman-return-openai/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=sam-altman-return-openai</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/11/22/sam-altman-return-openai/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 22 Nov 2023 06:20:36 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技趣聞]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[ChatGPT]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[microsoft]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[openai]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1205848</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>據《Bloomberg》報道， Microsoft 正在向 OpenAI 提出改革措施，以確保自身作為 OpenAI 最大投資者的權益。與此同時，Sam Altman 與 OpenAI 董事局成員及臨時行政總裁 Emmett Shear 磋商成功，OpenAI 在官方 X （前稱 Twitter）發文表示 Sam Altman 將會回歸 OpenAI 復任行政總裁一職，而 OpenAI 董事局亦迎來新成員。</p><p><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">We have reached an agreement in principle for Sam Altman to return to OpenAI as CEO with a new initial board of Bret Taylor (Chair), Larry Summers, and Adam D&#39;Angelo.<br><br>We are collaborating to figure out the details. Thank you so much for your patience through this.</p>&mdash; OpenAI (@OpenAI) <a href="https://twitter.com/OpenAI/status/1727206187077370115?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">November 22, 2023</a></blockquote><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div></p><p>上週六 OpenAI 董事局宣佈解僱 Sam Altman 後，全球正密切關注 Sam Altman 會否重返 OpenAI 繼續擔任行政總裁。今日（22 日）據《Bloomberg》報道，OpenAI 最大投資者 Microsoft 亦正式插手這次事件。稍早前 OpenAI 在官方 X 宣佈 Sam Altman 將會回歸 OpenAI ，同時 OpenAI 將迎來全新董事局成員，包括董事局主席 Bret Taylor、Larry Summer 及 Adam D&#8217;Angelo。</p><p>現階段 OpenAI 表示仍然在商討相關細節，但可以確定的是 Sam Altman 會回歸 OpenAI。</p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://www.blocktempo.com/microsoft-is-discussing-governance-changes-it-wants-from-openai/">Block Tempo</a>、<a href="https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-21/microsoft-discussing-governance-changes-it-wants-from-openai#xj4y7vzkg">Bloomberg</a>、<a href="https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-21/altman-openai-board-open-talks-to-negotiate-his-possible-return">Bloomberg</a>、 <a href="https://twitter.com/OpenAI/status/1727206187077370115">OpenAI@X</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" a